				<outline text="HBD @holy_schnitt ✨🍾🎈" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 23:21:29 GMT" tweetId="1409653206108438532" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409653206108438532" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="California’s yoga, wellness and spirituality community has a QAnon problem https://t.co/phLE0MRN1B" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 20:41:17 GMT" tweetId="1409612892094095365" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409612892094095365" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="So impressed with @theinformation @kyurieff really useful Creator Economy startup database. I'm sure they'll be adding lots more as this sector continue to boom https://t.co/6DVeMk8vOo" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 20:01:19 GMT" tweetId="1409602833968635911" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409602833968635911" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="BI's @arperelli @dwhate @SydneyKBradley @margauxmaccoll have also made some excellent databases/lists that are totally worth the sub! Here's one they did of top investors/VCs in the influencer industry feat @ljin18 @rex_woodbury @conniechan and more! https://t.co/gfHmbbwIkN" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 20:06:14 GMT" tweetId="1409604071930044421" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409604071930044421" inReplyToId="1409602833968635911" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
