				<outline text="&quot;Saying Near 'took their life' is giving these people an out for their actions, which directly resulted in the intentional death of a person.&quot; https://t.co/oqXRKoOjbl" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:43:30 GMT" tweetId="1409598349787893762" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409598349787893762" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="There's no such thing as a coincidence, the fact that you're reading this tweet means you're energetically aligned with me and this message" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:37:11 GMT" tweetId="1409596761098768393" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409596761098768393" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Let him do it https://t.co/Vpa8LCIGeb" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:36:46 GMT" tweetId="1409596654089478145" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409596654089478145" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text=".@kathrynfiona on the digital-media-to-Netflix pipeline and more https://t.co/Ut5UpG4iBG" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:28:57 GMT" tweetId="1409594688588365824" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409594688588365824" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Only in the past year has the tech industry as a whole started to recognize influencers as businesses (and many still have sexist notions &quot;influencer&quot; is vs &quot;creator,&quot; which are the same thing). I think as the space continues to grow in terms of $ more ppl will recognize it! https://t.co/iEoocBC5ng" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:21:32 GMT" tweetId="1409592821804244997" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409592821804244997" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="There are actually several LLCs called Instagram Husband or some version of that I'm sorry to report 😅 https://t.co/hQLdCJgvro https://t.co/cdWOclw5RZ" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:10:53 GMT" tweetId="1409590142864486401" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409590142864486401" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="FaZe Clan, Jeffree Star, MrBeast, Arielle Charnas and MANY more influencers received PPP loans. I know people don't like to think of it this way but creator-led companies are the fastest growing type of small business! https://t.co/ZGmePOwsnm" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 19:14:09 GMT" tweetId="1409590964570656768" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409590964570656768" inReplyToId="1409590142864486401" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Meet me by the 6-foot bronze Elon Musk statue in nyc https://t.co/rYWEXE9dMv" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:38:48 GMT" tweetId="1409566968617734147" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409566968617734147" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="Bidding 1 zillion dollars so I can ship this statue to @kenklippenstein's living room  https://t.co/sjk70ZN1hh" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 18:13:29 GMT" tweetId="1409575696322600962" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409575696322600962" inReplyToId="1409566968617734147" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
					</outline>
				<outline text="Are you a print reader? Donate your extra stacks of clean papers to the @wildbirdfund! https://t.co/rHkmSOXCI0" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:14:22 GMT" tweetId="1409560821546450944" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409560821546450944" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="You get a term sheet https://t.co/g6Pd6EceLd" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:05:55 GMT" tweetId="1409558694778392579" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409558694778392579" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
				<outline text="Ppl need to understand that &quot;exposing/deep dive&quot; videos almost universally have an agenda, where things are twisted to fit a narrative and all &quot;evidence&quot; is in service of promoting that narrative. These videos mimic the language of reporting but are nothing like actual journalism https://t.co/obZr4PY181" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 16:51:35 GMT" tweetId="1409555085827268609" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409555085827268609" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
					<outline text="I'd say generally don't trust anything you watch on YouTube. It's a lead distributor of conspiracy theories, propaganda, and disinfo. Try to read a book on the topic by an expert or go to verified sources like a reputable news outlet or expert in the space https://t.co/8Ew3dazGUF" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:01:09 GMT" tweetId="1409557493655638021" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409557493655638021" inReplyToId="1409555085827268609" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" >
						<outline text="Way too many young people blindly trust things they've seen on YouTube the way too many boomers trust everything they read on FB" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 17:13:07 GMT" tweetId="1409560506365472768" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409560506365472768" inReplyToId="1409557493655638021" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="How YouTube’s rules are used to silence human rights activists https://t.co/HJoXXLSh19" type="tweet" created="Mon, 28 Jun 2021 16:47:25 GMT" tweetId="1409554037037404164" urltweet="https://twitter.com/taylorlorenz/status/1409554037037404164" tweetUserName="taylorlorenz" />
